SUMMARY:Bolo Boys at Wild Heaven Brewing — Dog Days at Wild Heaven
DESCRIPTION:We're glad to keep the collaboration with Wild Heaven Avondale
  rolling — Dirty Shame\, Acoustic Station\, Ante Up\, and the Bolo Boys 
 back on Maple Street for about three and a half hours of music. We'll play
  inside or outside depending on the weather\, but either way you can count
  on a good time: good music\, good food\, and good beer. Free\, all ages 
 — come hang out.
